<div class='panel'>This Mastodon instance is managed from The Netherlands, but can be used by any nationality. No restrictions on languages. <br>
Admin only speaks Dutch/English/German and a little French.
<br>
Launched April 12th, 2017.
<br>
The server runs on an Amazon AWS server, and is monitored for capacity / load. It can be extended if needed.<br>
Also, daily backups are created and stored in a different location.
<br>
<br>
Rules are easy:<br>
No illegal or offensive content. 
<br>
<br>
<a href=https://paypal.me/schilders>Donations</a> are welcome for maintaining and expanding the server.</div>
